(20, 1, '2024-03-29 06:32:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Namaste and welcome to Buddy Hikers, a leading adventure sports company operating in the beautiful state of Uttarakhand. We are a team of experienced professionals who are passionate about exploring the great outdoors and providing the best adventure sports experience to our clients.\r\nAt Buddy Hikers, we take pride in our commitment to reliability and responsible tourism. We understand that when you plan an adventure trip, it is important that you can rely on us to keep our promises and ensure that your trip runs smoothly. We also recognize the importance of sustainable tourism and work towards minimizing our impact on the environment while contributing positively to the local communities.\r\nReliability:\r\nWhen you book a trip with Buddy Hikers, you can trust us to keep our commitments. We understand that your time is valuable, and we ensure that our trips depart on time as scheduled. Our team works hard to plan and coordinate the logistics of your trip so that you can focus on enjoying your adventure. We also prioritize safety and reliability above everything else, and we never compromise on these values.\r\nResponsible Tourism:\r\nBuddy Hikers is committed to responsible tourism, and we integrate sustainable development principles in all aspects of our business. We believe that our core purpose is to provide our clients with authentic experiences while respecting the people, cultures, and environments of the places we visit. Our values are not just words on paper, but they are ingrained in our culture and daily operations. We expect our staff and clients to follow the principles of responsible travel and contribute to sustainable development.\r\nOur Exclusive Projects:\r\nAt Buddy Hikers, we have developed exclusive projects to ensure that we maintain the highest standards of safety, environmental awareness, and efficiency.\r\nTraining Programs for Crews:\r\nWe understand that our crew\'s efficiency is directly related to the safety of our clients. Therefore, we conduct regular training programs to keep our crew members updated on the latest developments in mountain trekking, climbing, and first-aid treatment related to mountain sickness. We also provide language training to our staff members to ensure clear communication with our clients. We believe that a well-trained and knowledgeable crew is essential for a successful and safe adventure trip.\r\nEnvironmental Awareness Training for Our Business Associates and Crews:\r\nBuddy Hikers is committed to minimizing our impact on the environment and using resources in a responsible and efficient manner. We train our business associates and crew members to identify locally-owned and operated services and use public transport where possible to reduce fuel usage. We also encourage the conservation of water and support initiatives that promote its conservative use. Our team encourages our clients to eat locally produced food and goods to reduce the embodied energy of the food and goods purchased by our guests. We also promote the use of refillable water bottles to minimize waste disposal issues.\r\nConclusion:\r\nBuddy Hikers is a leading adventure sports company operating in Uttarakhand. We are committed to providing our clients with authentic and safe adventure experiences while contributing positively to the local communities and the environment. Our team of professionals is passionate about exploring the great outdoors and ensuring that you have the best adventure sports experience. Thank you for considering Buddy Hikers for your next adventure trip.\r\n\r\nOur CEO, Rakesh Singh Sajwan, leads our team with a passion for adventure and a dedication to responsible tourism. We hope you\'ll join us on a journey that not only provides an unforgettable experience, but also supports the local community and environment.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nThe Buddy Hikers Team', '', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2024-03-29 06:32